name: Team Members Block in Team Configuration page
objective: Team Members Block in Team Configuration page

customFields.Priority P1 to P4: P4 - Low-Impact (Edge or unsuitable to repeat?)

inline.description:
1. Login to System Console as sysadmin user and visit Teams Page.
2. Click on any team which is not LDAP Group Synced.
3. Check the Members block is displayed and list of members in the team is correctly displayed.
inline.expectedResult: 3. Members block should be displayed in the Team Configuration page and the list of members should be displayed correctly.
